---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Energy &amp; Performance IV Therapy | Menon Medispa | Millburn, NJ"
  description="Energy and performance IV drip therapy in Millburn NJ. Boost metabolism, enhance mental clarity, and accelerate muscle recovery with our customized energy infusions."
>
  <main class="sp" data-slug="energy-performance">

    <section class="sp-hero" aria-label="Energy &amp; Performance IV Therapy in Millburn NJ">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-hero__grid">
          <div class="sp-hero__content">
            <h1 class="sp-hero__title">Energy &amp; Performance IV Therapy in Millburn NJ</h1>
            <p class="sp-hero__eyebrow">Unlock your peak potential with sustained energy and mental clarity.</p>
            <p class="sp-hero__lead">Fight fatigue, brain fog, and slow workout recovery. Our Energy &amp; Performance IV drip in Millburn, NJ, delivers a direct infusion of vitamins and amino acids to boost your metabolism, enhance focus, and improve athletic performance.</p>
            <div class="sp-hero__actions">
              <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Book Your IV Therapy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-reviews">
              <div class="sp-reviews__avatars">
                <img src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
              </div>
              <div class="sp-reviews__text">
                <span class="sp-reviews__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
                <span class="sp-reviews__count">100+ 5 Star Reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="sp-hero__img" src="/images/33f6a2a1c88f.png" alt="Energy &amp; Performance IV Therapy in Millburn NJ" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-badges" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="sp-container sp-badges__row">
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Boost Your Metabolism</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Enhance Mental Clarity</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Accelerate Muscle Recovery</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain" aria-label="Formulas">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Choose Your Formula</h2>
          <div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">ENERGY Signature</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for a fast-acting, targeted boost to fight fatigue and sharpen mental focus.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This drip is packed with a powerful blend of essential vitamins and minerals to form the foundation of your energy boost.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>B12 &amp; Taurine: The core drivers for firing up your metabolism and providing a clean, sustained energy boost.</li><li>Vitamin C &amp; Glutathione: Powerful antioxidants that reduce the cellular stress and "crash" feeling associated with fatigue.</li><li>Minerals: Essential electrolytes to ensure optimal hydration and cellular function.</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">ENERGY Deluxe</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for comprehensive metabolic support, sustained athletic performance, and faster recovery.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This all-in-one formula provides full-spectrum support for your body's entire energy production cycle. Includes a foundation of antioxidants &amp; B12, plus:</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Complete B-Complex (B5, Niacin, etc.): A full suite of B-vitamins essential for converting food into usable, long-lasting energy.</li><li>Magnesium &amp; Zinc: Critical minerals that support muscle function, aid in faster recovery, and help prevent cramping.</li><li>Amino Acids: The fundamental building blocks for repairing muscle tissue after workouts and sustaining endurance.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-photos" aria-label="Customer Photos">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-photos__head"><h2>Hear From Our Customers!</h2></div>
        <div class="sp-photos__grid">
          <img src="/images/9ebaca3843d3.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/6c461885a28e.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/823792ea5ead.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/cd675890fe0d.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/2e5d1e68225a.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain sp-plain--alt" aria-label="Process">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">01</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Personalized Consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">02</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Relax and Recharge</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">03</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Feel the Benefits</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Many clients report immediate benefits after their session. The nutrients continue to work for days, supporting your body's natural processes and helping you feel and look your best.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-pricing" aria-label="Pricing">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-pricing__head">
          <h2>Book Your IV Therapy</h2>
          <p style="font-style:italic;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">All IV Drips are 500ml. Upgrade to 1000ml for only $25</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-pricelist">
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/537a32cc1127.avif" alt="ENERGY (Signature)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/energy-signature">ENERGY (Signature)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/energy-signature">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$200</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/energy-signature">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/537a32cc1127.avif" alt="ENERGY (Deluxe)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/energy-deluxe">ENERGY (Deluxe)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/energy-deluxe">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$250</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/energy-deluxe">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-testimonial" aria-label="What Our Clients Say">
      <img class="sp-testimonial__bg" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="sp-testimonial__overlay"></div>
      <div class="sp-container sp-testimonial__inner">
        <h2 class="sp-script-title sp-script-title--light" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">What Our <em>Clients</em> Say</h2>
        <blockquote class="sp-quote">
          <span class="sp-quote__mark">&ldquo;</span>
          Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.
          <cite>Alexa C.</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <img src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="5 Star Google Reviews" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" style="margin-top:1.75rem;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-faq__card">
          <div class="sp-faq__head"><h2 class="sp-faq__title">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
          <div class="sp-faq__list">
            <details class="sp-faq__item" open>
              <summary>Who is a good candidate for an Energy &amp; Performance drip?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>This drip is ideal for anyone looking to overcome fatigue and brain fog, including busy professionals, frequent travelers, and students. It's also highly effective for athletes or fitness enthusiasts seeking to enhance performance, improve endurance, and accelerate post-workout recovery.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How is this different from drinking coffee or an energy drink?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>While caffeine provides a temporary, stimulant-based jolt, our IV therapy delivers essential vitamins and amino acids directly to your cells for true, sustainable energy. There are no jitters and no crash—just a clean, vibrant feeling of enhanced focus and vitality.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>Is it better to get this IV drip before or after a workout?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>It depends on your goal. A pre-workout drip can help hydrate you and prepare your muscles for peak performance. A post-workout drip is excellent for rehydration, reducing muscle soreness, and accelerating the recovery process.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How often should I get an IV drip for sustained energy?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>For general energy maintenance, a session every 2-4 weeks is effective for many clients. Athletes may choose to schedule sessions more frequently around major training periods or competitions.</p></div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-cta" aria-label="Ready to Operate at 100%?">
      <div class="sp-container sp-cta__grid">
        <div class="sp-cta__copy">
          <h2 class="sp-cta__title">Ready to Operate at 100%?</h2>
          <p class="sp-cta__sub">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
          <p>Stop settling for tired afternoons and slow recovery. Discover what your body is truly capable of with our advanced IV therapy. Schedule your complimentary consultation today.</p>
          <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-cta__media">
          <img src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
